{"tid":1601243,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"印象中除咗612之外，每次集會連登都有話和理非一日","createTime":"2019-09-29T03:25:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T03:38:39.000Z","uid":207710,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"3b7e8576e0f4aaee697b72f6f508ee17e9f1bf2a","tid":1601243,"uid":207710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T03:25:53.000Z","msg":"咁仲叫唔叫和理非一日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n抑或係政府想止暴制亂嘅計謀<br />\n和勇合一唔再和勇合一<br />\n而係全部活動回歸和理非<br />\n好似鳩嗚團咁行到散？<br />\n<br />\n唔係話今日唔應該和理非<br />\n而係希望大家講「目標已到，Be water」、「今日和理非一日，唔好令運動失焦」之前<br />\n反思自己有無理解過勇武背後嘅rationale<br />\n定係由此至終只係諗自己條戰線？<br />\n<br />\n唔想令運動失焦可以有好多方法<br />\n口號上調整，文宣方向上調整、衝突強度上嘅調整<br />\n但一刀切喺所有集會遊行都叫「和理非一日」<br />\n絕對唔係通盤理性考量下嘅結論"},{"pid":"7706689c9b90f1057ef082962bc58ef082f76403","tid":1601243,"uid":207710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T03:26:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c4ee73a791342deee1df2cf83914dc76457bc106","tid":1601243,"uid":207710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T03:26:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bccf98ee12fc2b7fd04832a93b570ebbb9573747","tid":1601243,"uid":207710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T03:27:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c3a2b9761b34e7b0da6483bd594f2d0502e3f6ee","tid":1601243,"uid":207710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T03:27:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"74479462002ba081c12a60a599d7ee89b184b044","tid":1601243,"uid":207710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T03:28:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"96487a0ed8826997073959ffaac7532756529696","tid":1601243,"uid":324701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T03:28:24.000Z","msg":"策略上想和理非一日啫~~俾外國睇要關公呀嘛<br />\n不過現實好難做到係真嘅"},{"pid":"32b8e52ff42f01772a3b1024d092448860aef07f","tid":1601243,"uid":94771,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T03:29:08.000Z","msg":"其實